{"id": 578, "genre": 1000, "title": "经典动漫设定，哪个最令你迷醉？", "description": "就好像，“最后一分钟拯救”之于好莱坞，“做人最重要的就是开心”之于 TVB，一样的存在。", "record_count": 8546, "comment_count": 71, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160608143557aRTyDcjMUV0xnZYh.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-21T01:13:41Z", "questions": [{"id": 477, "title": "经典动漫设定，哪个最令你迷醉？", "content": "令人迷醉的动漫设定", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 16995, "content": "很多角色食量都超大，且疑似饭量和能量成正比", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193401wZjfxLNUQzF9TdvA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 16996, "content": "一直一直用着翻盖手机", "image": "img/option/option/201606071934029QjF3Z6hYVX2zqpG.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 16997, "content": "赶时间都一定要咬着吐司出现", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193402YyiwpF3Q9bOJqmAo.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 16998, "content": "校园主角的座位一定是靠窗倒数第二排的神之座位", "image": "img/option/option/20160608143323lvx8PosHiV7GTDLF.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 16999, "content": "主角通常都没有父母", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193402MTBXF8HNxfnAyapP.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17000, "content": "主角通常要被打到快死掉才开启外挂模式", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193402eUcgNdIZJqCsM9xn.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17002, "content": "主角也不一定要有多强的能力，但是嘴炮功力绝对是一流的", "image": "img/option/option/201606071937363FMX064OTBntSpNd.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17003, "content": "反派一般都比较单纯，理想不是毁灭全人类就是征服全世界", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193403P49uHyJRAEeVlr8i.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17008, "content": "眼镜总反光的基本是个腹黑的变态", "image": "img/option/option/20160608143324qxTrVBwFPsQjvn4g.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}